---
title: Chimichurri Steak with Roasted Pepper, Tomato, & Couscous Salad
description: Chimichurri—an Argentine herb sauce—is one of the most flavorful condiments out there. We’re making it with mild parsley and chili flakes for a kick. A touch of cumin and charred roasted peppers gives this couscous salad a slightly smoky flavor—it’s perfect with juicy, pan-seared steak.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56b3b0e6fd2cb94a3a8b4567.jpg
